## Best Practices

1. **Keep docs updated** - Update documentation when code changes
2. **Use examples** - Include code examples in documentation
3. **Explain why** - Document decisions and rationale
4. **Be concise** - Keep documentation clear and brief
5. **Use consistent format** - Follow project documentation style
6. **Document public APIs** - Always document exported functions/types
7. **Keep comments close** - Place comments near relevant code
